Summer Farmer’s Market Watercolor Postcard if you are looking for it, we recommend it Summer Farmer’s Market Watercolor Postcard You can order itSend someone a special note with this seasonal Farmer’s Market postcard featuring an original watercolor painting of a quaint, country farm market of homemade goods and veggies for sale! The Henhouse Farm Market, features a cute, colorful summer store full of fresh vegetables, canned goods, bakery items, and local crafts. A quiet scene, this enticing storefront has just opened, and the farmers are busy harvesting melons, gathering fresh eggs, and baking pies with handpicked berries. Two free range chickens roam out front, ready to greet the first customer of the day. A truly unique card for anyone, this little bit of mail was inspired by my favorite Virginia markets and created as the August page of a calendar and doubles as frameable artwork. Blank on the inside for writing a note to friends and family. Price:$2.05
